Commentr is an app that generates articles, and populates them with comments

The database can be deleted using the command:
"python3 manage.py flush"

Articles, users, and comments are generated using the command:
"python3 manage.py gen_everything"

Additional comments can be added using:
"python3 manage.py gen_comments"

Comments are automatically filtered using a dictionary of profanity.
This, among all other dictionaries for random generation are located in the
"./dictionaries" directory

A mod queue to review and enable/disable comments is available using:
"python3 manage.py comments_queue"
But is requires an administrator account.

Billing to companies is on a per comment rate, and can be calculated using:
"python3 manage.py bill_companies"
